OL,3,CPatient dies after falling from
OL,4,Chospital roof in Swansea
OL,6,FA patient has died after falling off
OL,7,Fthe roof of Morriston Hospital in
OL,8,FSwansea.
OL,10,FPolice had been called to reports that
OL,11,Fa patient had made their way onto the
OL,12,Froof at 11.44pm on Friday, 16 August,
OL,13,Fwith a specialist negotiator deployed
OL,14,Fto engage with the patient: a 58-year-
OL,15,Fold man from Port Talbot.
