OL,3,CPatient dies after falling from
OL,4,Chospital roof in Swansea
OL,6,FA statement from South Wales Police
OL,7,Fsaid: "We received a report that a
OL,8,Fpatient at Morriston Hospital had made
OL,9,Fhis way onto the roof of the building.
OL,10,FUnfortunately, shortly after 3.20am
OL,11,Fthe man jumped from the roof suffering
OL,12,Ffatal injuries."
OL,14,FIt added that enquiries are on-going
OL,15,Fto establish the full circumstances of
OL,16,Fthe incident, adding: "The force has
OL,17,Fsince referred itself to the
OL,18,FIndependent Office for Police Conduct
OL,19,Fas is usual in such matters."
