OL,3,CPatient dies after falling from
OL,4,Chospital roof in Swansea
OL,6,FA Swansea Bay Health Board
OL,7,Fspokesperson said: "We are deeply
OL,8,Fsaddened to confirm that there was a
OL,9,Ffatality at Morriston Hospital in the
OL,10,Fearly hours of Saturday morning
OL,11,Ffollowing the abscondment of a patient
OL,12,Fwho was due to be transferred to
OL,13,Fanother location.
OL,15,F"Police and fire brigade were in
OL,16,Fattendance but despite their efforts
OL,17,Fand those of our staff, the patient
OL,18,Fcould not be saved."
